1. Prepare image(s)
2. Process image with processor to get `pixel_values`
3. Process text/question with tokenizer to get `input_ids`, `attention_mask`, etc.
4. Pass BOTH to model.generate()
5. Decode model output using tokenizer
6. Parse/format final output

